&gt; &lt;OLD&gt;
&gt;
&gt; Tucson looks around at those who were paying attention and nods to them.
&gt;
&gt; &quot; Freedom is the right of all sentient beings.  And if I can achieve that,
&gt; rest assured yours will come too.  On the off chance that one of you might
&gt; be up against me, just play along with what Magmatron demands and I will cue
&gt; you in on what to do next.  All we need to do is think around him.  Do the
&gt; exact opposite of what he may expect out of us.  Unpredictability is our
&gt; best hope of escape.  How many more of you are willing to join us in our
&gt; escape plot?&quot;
&gt;
&gt; He looks down to Mach Kick with a smile.
&gt;
&gt; &quot; You&#39;re definitely onto something, keep up the good work.&quot;
&gt;

&lt;NEW&gt;

As TUSCON asked his question about who was with him in his endevor,
the remaining three others raised their appendeges as well.

BIG CONVOY nodded back at them. &quot;Those are part of my team as well.&quot;
He said, his voice quiet and low. &quot;The orange one is my second in
command, Longrack, the other two are my Recon officer Stampy and
Sharpedge who is adept at land and water combat.&quot;

The three soldiers nod at CONVOY and then  at TUSCON.

&gt; &lt;OLD&gt;
&gt;
&gt; With a gentile rub on Mach&#39;s shoulder, Tucson then joins Big Convoy and
&gt; follows him to the chamber.
&gt;
&gt; &quot; I need to ask you something, the Matrix, I fear it&#39;s in danger of
&gt; corruption, is Dark Rodimus holding it in his possession?  If so I must be
&gt; permitted to battle him for the Matrix, so I can deliver it to more capable
&gt; hands. If I don&#39;t make it out, promise me you will take it to Leo Prime
&gt; where it will be safe?&quot;

&lt;NEW&gt;

BIG CONVOY gave TUSCON a long searching look before he nodded. &quot;You
believe that Dark Rodimus still has the matrix?&quot; CONVOY nodded
thoughtfully.

He turned to look at TUSCON, &quot;I don&#39;t know if he has it or not, but
Magmatron undoubtedly has some purpose for keeping him around. From
what I gather he is being trained and groomed by Magmatron himself and
I hear he is quite skilled in the art of combat.&quot;

CONVOY grunted, &quot;I don&#39;t have much control over who fights and when.&quot;
He said in gruff tones. &quot;But I will do what I can to do to give you
your shot.&quot;

